Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:47.70,OP JP,,0,0,0,,れぼるじゃーん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.90,0:00:51.30,OP JP,,0,0,0,,そんじゃ手始めに  革命しましょ  ご準備
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:57.80,OP JP,,0,0,0,,(Hello, nice to meet you, yeah!)
